# RwDrv.sys ![:inline](/images/twitter_verified.png) 


### Description

RwDrv.sys is a vulnerable driver and more information will be added as found.
- **UUID**: b03798af-d25a-400b-9236-4643a802846f
- **Created**: 2023-05-06
- **Author**: Nasreddine Bencherchali
- **Acknowledgement**: [] | [](https://twitter.com/)

{{< button "https://github.com/magicsword-io/LOLDrivers/raw/main/drivers/f853abe0dc162601e66e4a346faed854.bin" "Download" >}}
{{< tip "warning" >}}
This download link contains the vulnerable driver!

{{< /tip >}}

### Commands

```
sc.exe create RwDrv.sys binPath=C:\windows\temp\RwDrv.sys type=kernel &amp;&amp; sc.exe start RwDrv.sys
```


| Use Case | Privileges | Operating System | 
|:---- | ---- | ---- |
| Elevate privileges | kernel | Windows 10 |
